@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Blow Out!";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Welcome to Blow Out!</h1>
    <p>
        We are a musical instrument rental company. We currently offer rentals for trumpets, trombones, tubas, flutes, clarinets, and saxophones. Customers can choose to rent new or used instruments. One benefit of renting from our company is that you have the opportunity to gain ownership of an instrument after renting it for 18 months. Thanks for considering us for your instrument rental needs!
    </p>
    <br />
    <p class="lead">"It's easy to play any musical instrument: all you have to do is touch the right key at the right time and the instrument will play itself”.  - Johann Sebastian Bach</p>
    <p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x_t1sR8_NKQ" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Why you should join band! &raquo;</a></p>
</div>

